data_table.description: This sample attributes table includes body site where sample was collected, analyte type, tumor status, sequencing center, funding source, TOPMed phase, project, and study name.

variable.name: BODY_SITE
variable.description: Body site where sample was collected

variable.name: IS_TUMOR
variable.description: Whether or not sample came from a tumor tissue

variable.name: SEQUENCING_CENTER
variable.description: Name of the center which conducted sequencing

variable.name: TOPMed_Project
variable.description: TOPMed-assigned short study name (1:1 with TOPMed phs number)
